text="Basis with decidable bottomhood yields positive generation">Basis with decidable bottomhood yields positive generation</fr:title><fr:taxon>Corollary</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> be a pointed continuous dcpo presented by a basis <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[B\subseteq  A]]></fr:tex> for each element <fr:tex
